<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10270453>
    dc:description "Figure 1. Phaonantho benevola Couri, 1979. Male: (A) Head, frontal view. (B) Habitus, dorsal view. (C) Habitus, lateral view. Female: (D) Head, frontal view. (E) Habitus,dorsal view.(F) Habitus,lateral view.Scale bar:1.0 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10270453/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10270463>
    dc:description "Figure 4. Map of Phaonantho species with geopolitical borders: P. benevola (orange); P.mallochi (blue); P.sordilloae (red); and Phaonantho sp. (black). Circles = literature records;square = new records." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10270463/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

